*******************************************************************************
viewmacro	-  display a macro in a popup window
*******************************************************************************

  This command displays a macro in a popup window.
  An appdir search is used to find the macro.
  To display an arbitrary file with a absolute
  pathname, use the viewman macro.
  viewmacro is not available on MacOS

  Usage  -  viewmacro('jexp1')  // display the jexp1 macro
